<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-left: 33.120000000000005pt;margin-right: 2.400000000000091pt;margin-top:1.2pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 9.7444pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">enable Chefs to create AT TABLE Invitations for AT TABLE Events and for Diners to learn about and book AT TABLE Events. You understand and agree that AT TABLE is not a party to any agreements between Chefs and / or Diners and that AT TABLE has no control over (and therefore not liable or obligated to you in respect of) the conduct of (i) Chefs, (ii) Diners, (iii) other users of the AT TABLE Websites and AT TABLE Services or (iv) others attending or facilitating AT TABLE Events. You agree that AT TABLE is not responsible for any damage or harm resulting from your interactions with other users of the AT TABLE Websites or AT TABLE Services and you accept that (to the maximum extent permitted by law) AT TABLE disclaims all liability resulting from the conduct or any such person.&nbsp;</span></p>
